items.title: Awesome Ipfs
items.content_text:
### Apps

*   [archiveweb.page (‚≠ê1k)](https://github.com/webrecorder/archiveweb.page) - A High-Fidelity Web Archiving Extension for Chrome and Chromium based browsers with support for IPFS.
*   [brig (‚≠ê574)](https://github.com/sahib/brig) - File synchronization with git like interface and FUSE filesystem.
*   [Diffuse (‚≠ê837)](https://github.com/icidasset/diffuse) - Play music from your IPFS node, or any other cloud/distributed storage service you use.
*   [IPFS Desktop (‚≠ê6.3k)](https://github.com/ipfs-shipyard/ipfs-desktop) - IPFS Desktop gives you all the power of IPFS in a convenient desktop app: a complete IPFS node, plus handy OS menubar/taskbar shortcuts and an all-in-one file manager, peer map, and content explorer.

### Tools

*   [git-ipfs-rehost (‚≠ê201)](https://github.com/whyrusleeping/git-ipfs-rehost) - A script to rehost your git repos in ipfs.
*   [Git IPFS Remote Bridge (‚≠ê25)](https://github.com/ElettraSciComp/Git-IPFS-Remote-Bridge) - set of programs written in Python 3 which allow Git user to clone, push, fetch, self-host or release Git repositories over IPFS decentralized data storage system.
*   [ipfs-publish (‚≠ê67)](https://github.com/auhau/ipfs-publish/) - Continuous Delivery tool for delivery of static websites from Git providers to IPFS.
*   [ipfs-video-gateway (‚≠ê46)](https://github.com/bneijt/ipfs-video-gateway) - Cloud-init your own IPFS gateway on a cloud provider and easily pin content through a simple web interface.
*   [SimpleAsWater Bot (‚≠ê13)](https://github.com/simpleaswater/twitter-pinbot) - A twitter bot that adds, pins, unpins your tweets to public IPFS network using IPFS Cluster.

### Services & Platforms

*   [Ceramic](https://ceramic.network/) - Ceramic combines IPFS content addressing with advanced cryptography and blockchain timestamps to guarantee security and verifiability of data.

### Pinning services

*   [Pinata](https://pinata.cloud) - Build and manage your dapp through Pinata‚Äôs REST API and IPFS toolkit.
